                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Both job applicants (aka interviewers) and industry professionals (aka interviewees) sign up on intervyouer.com</li>
                                        <li>Job Applicants picks an interviewer from the pool of interviewers and schedules an interview with him/her</li>
                                        <li>Once the job applicant schedules an interview, an interview request is sent to the relevant interviewer</li>
                                        <li>Interviewer will accept/decline the interview request and accordingly the job applicant will be notiied</li>
                                        <li>If the interviewer accepts the interview, an interview will be conducted on intervyouer.com</li>
                                        <li>An interviewer submits feedback to the job applicant and job applicant also gets a chance to rate the interviewer</li>
